<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>VLLM on Pan Binghong's Tech Blog</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/tags/vllm/</link><description>Recent content in VLLM on Pan Binghong's Tech Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.159.2</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 03:47:46 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/tags/vllm/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Learning vLL (0.7.2) with Cursor</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/ai/learning-vll-0.7.2-with-cursor/</link><pubDate>Mon, 14 Apr 2025 00:38:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/ai/learning-vll-0.7.2-with-cursor/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;💡 之前一直用cursor辅助写代码，突然试了一下去利用cursor来学代码，发现效果嘎嘎好。这里记录一下比较火的vllm中提升推理速度的一些关键代码。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h1 id="1-what-is-vllm"&gt;1. What is vLLM？&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/fc187c04-cf34-444f-b5f2-bdcdfad76660/ccc90792-56ef-4142-8b21-8ecb32787141/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB4664GN7XASA%2F20260402%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260402T034537Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEJv%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQCjO9RO5l8Sc84H63qMGGYaXGb%2F8J4QbRmy9Uu2ODZDZAIgQUgJfz8oAqXjN2ug2xG4h767euXLV3iqMj%2F8IPezsV4q%2FwMIZBAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDHya%2FKknvVvtbWTs1ircA2Cb%2BvdKnhpGft4rOyA23rZlYNvxQuuJF6MWKHhfC0pItTfwA50R6J0u2Q9%2BhNOixJL6Rv37iTyeC5MZDG%2FzdESDlZKRZcx3wjfXT6u07hbCuUrB81jx%2B7P0drxjX4JxyEaSuDy0N4iPjO5M5PWfRnVgR%2BqebrUYEiAcgTj%2FYwOL1Nz15vPboktWwfE0omuuNMZb9UA0DIG8d9jfhNhO%2F3nCP5CV6bxQilfo7iSnY2xDBRGbyGwTqzt2cKe3j%2Bfyns5hZiena5qWIGwup5hax3jGDwnhXAUBNntw6Djf0eZrNcEdWBeuUNe%2BTnx60EKPD%2FUnL0fyUt5vVy%2B5l3fZCpWHDFnlr0Z1PlqOXRjmce6g55Mcz%2Bx%2F%2FBCgVreWc%2Fq3bMHmgGLjm6WF89%2FyD%2FkAHlcBfCrhytz4l5xZnBomCazW8zPLeeVYDFZWsDE5trosXjsTgN1QH7UIgVydRpB8Wm85Mlzpt6unMQDD1a%2FZ8HDylkZ9uKOKlyuZYVBI5CbboRRUtwePtZNjnP1qg74%2BGy%2BtLJbLe0WHNFawnA7Oc3akAhDPATpk4PT9omVd%2B8kcmfxRmduSHuJTT9eXcPJ5nB%2BBhaugqaf4SpsMIK3rs0vjijx2y6RqfvgwIjVNMIuvt84GOqUBbdF1%2FrUGLx3JrLcJDWIgTUONgSCeiTsNSWipDg8Wc2ekT%2Ba9J4lgpZog1Ox3qujpkONbKxep6MUqHMbABsgOLESIyCH4Cf2RRyqLUocAfho6uH8tESl2MF%2BmZwJ6hGQngTImCMkfY1L%2BYTGM2ZpmBhu8SpAuzDXlXDc%2BPNtCoYcM7sgH%2FpyGDx80mZsDlwKOdHqm0huuukF%2Fo8bMPIXZo8yFqQok&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b2b6df5e83b7e78434809f82d8fe388a8a118ebfea1a7c23e18ae164dea977e6&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;vLLM是大模型推理加速框架。主要在KVcache管理中采用了PageAttention技术，支持市面上主流的开源大模型，支持量化类型为：GPTQ, AWQ, INT4, INT8, and FP8&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
